mage_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/4/26/DSC05999.jpg" /><br /><br />CINCINNATI – The No. 12 West Virginia University baseball team dropped the series finale to Cincinnati, 7-5, Sunday afternoon at UC Baseball Stadium. The Mountaineers fall to 28-12 overall and 13-8 in the Big 12 while the Bearcats improve 29-17 and 10-11 in conference play.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/26/DSC05999.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/26/DSC05999.jpg"><media:title>Dawson Montesa</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/26/DSC05999.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 18:05:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59047</s:story_id></item><item><title>Golf Heads to Big 12 Championship</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/26/golf-heads-to-big-12-championship</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/26/golf-heads-to-big-12-championship</guid><category>Golf</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Big 12 Championship" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/4/26/GOLF26_Matchup_1920x1080_Big12C.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University golf team will compete in the Big 12 Golf Championship from Monday to Wednesday in Hutchinson, Kansas.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/26/GOLF26_Matchup_1920x1080_Big12C.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/26/GOLF26_Matchup_1920x1080_Big12C.jpg"><media:title>Big 12 Championship</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/26/GOLF26_Matchup_1920x1080_Big12C.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 11:02:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>5</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59046</s:story_id></item><item><title>Mountaineers Win Conclusion of Friday's Game, Drop Second Game</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/25/baseball-mountaineers-win-conclusion-of-fridays-game-drop-second-game</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/25/baseball-mountaineers-win-conclusion-of-fridays-game-drop-second-game</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Maxwell Molessa swings and hits a go-ahead two-run single in the 13th inning against Cincinnati" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/4/25/DSC04920.jpg" /><br /><br />CINCINNATI (April 25, 2026) – Picking up in the 12th inning of a 5-5 game, the No. 12 West Virginia University baseball team scored four in the 13th to win the conclusion of the suspended game, 9-5, over Cincinnati. In the regularly scheduled contest, the Mountaineers fell to the Bearcats, 5-2, Saturday afternoon at UC Baseball Stadium.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/25/DSC04920.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/25/DSC04920.jpg"><media:title>Maxwell Molessa swings and hits a go-ahead two-run single in the 13th inning against Cincinnati</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/25/DSC04920.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 20:42:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59045</s:story_id></item><item><title>Game Against Cincinnati Suspended in 12th Inning</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/24/baseball-game-against-cincinnati-suspended-in-12th-inning</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/24/baseball-game-against-cincinnati-suspended-in-12th-inning</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Ryan Maggy fist bumps first base coach Jacob Garcia after hitting a single." src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/4/24/DSC04200.jpg" /><br /><br />CINCINNATI – Friday night's baseball game between No. 12 West Virginia and Cincinnati has been suspended due to rain in the bottom of the 12th inning with the score tied, 5-5. The game will resume on Saturday at 3 p.m., followed by the regularly scheduled game.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/24/DSC04200.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/24/DSC04200.jpg"><media:title>Ryan Maggy fist bumps first base coach Jacob Garcia after hitting a single.</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/24/DSC04200.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 21:41:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59044</s:story_id></item></channel></rss>